# Review and merge gates

Follow **`docs/agents/REVIEW_MERGE_GATES.md`** and root **`AGENTS.md`** § PR lifecycle.

- Agent tests **before** asking the human to test.
- Human **code review** **before** the agent’s **PR self-review**.
- Agent **re-tests** after self-review; then merge to **`dev`**, delete the feature branch.
- After merge on **`dev`**: ask the user to **close the chat**; optionally steer **backlog / features / bugs**.
